```

## 4. Flujo de capas

```text
HTTP request
  -> platform/security/JwtAuthenticationFilter
  -> backend/api-rest/controllers/*
  -> backend/api-core/processor/crud/*Processor
  -> backend/api-core/maps/specific/*Map
  -> backend/api-base/rest/services/*Service
  -> backend/api-base/persistence/repositories/*Repository
  -> backend/api-base/persistence/entities/*Entity
  -> MySQL

Respuesta:
Entity -> DTO -> Output record -> ResponseEntity JSON
```

Patron por entidad:

```yaml
entity_stack:
  Entity: backend/api-base/.../persistence/entities/XEntity.java
  Repository: backend/api-base/.../persistence/repositories/XRepository.java
  DTO: backend/api-base/.../rest/dto/XDTO.java
  Service: backend/api-base/.../rest/services/XService.java
  Input records: backend/api-core/.../records/input/entity/XInput.java
  Output record: backend/api-core/.../records/output/entity/XOutput.java
  Mapper: backend/api-core/.../maps/specific/XMap.java
  Processor: backend/api-core/.../processor/crud/XProcessor.java
  Controller: backend/api-rest/.../controllers/rest/XRestController.java
```

